    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Birds that frequent bodies of water or inhabit the margin of lakes, rivers, seas, or other water. May be used to specifically refer to only larger swimming birds, such as ducks, geese, and swans.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
